 Quick commands:                                                                                                                                       
  - npm run deploy - Build & deploy code changes to Lambda                                                                                              
  - npm run update-tools - Update tool schema in AgentCore Gateway (edit update-tools.sh to add new tools)                                              
  - npm run mcp - Run local MCP server (for your Claude Desktop)                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                        
  MCP URL:                                                                                                                                              
  https://ghost-agent-gateway-t18kxjosdh.gateway.bedrock-agentcore.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/mcp                                                          
                                                                                                                                                        
  To add a new tool:                                                                                                                                    
  1. Add the tool in src/mcp-server.ts                                                                                                                  
  2. Edit update-tools.sh to include the new tool schema                                                                                                
  3. Run npm run deploy then npm run update-tools 